Package ie.isde

Class BoundingBox

java.lang.Object
ie.isde.BoundingBox
public class BoundingBox extends Object
Describes a spatial extent as a combination of its maximum and minimum points in latitue and longitude.

    • to_schema_org

      public String to_schema_org()
      Creates a string of JSON for inclusin in a Schema.orf serialisation of content. If the BoundingBox has non-equal north/south and east/west pairs then a GeoShape box is output, otherwise GeoCoordinates are used to specify the location of a Point.
      Returns:
      A JSON formatted string which represents the relevant serialisation of the BoundingBox
